{"type":"message","id":"e0072250","parentId":"f325234a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:59:27.013Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我找到了配置文件。让我看看尚书省（shangshu）的配置：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"shangshu\",\n  \"label\": \"尚书省\",\n  \"role\": \"尚书令\",\n  \"duty\": \"派单与升级裁决\",\n  \"emoji\": \"📮\",\n  \"model\": \"zai_shangshu/glm-4.7\",\n  \"defaultModel\": \"zai/glm-5\",\n  \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-shangshu\",\n  \"skills\": [],\n  \"allowAgents\": [\n    \"zhongshu\",\n    \"menxia\",\n    \"hubu\",\n    \"libu\",\n    \"bingbu\",\n    \"xingbu\",\n    \"gongbu\",\n    \"libu_hr\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n尚书省的allowAgents包括：\n- zhongshu（中书省）\n- menxia（门下省）\n- hubu（户部）\n- libu（礼部）\n- bingbu（兵部）\n- xingbu（刑部）\n- gongbu（工部）\n- libu_hr（吏部）\n\n所以配置文件确实显示尚书省有spawn六部的权限！\n\n但是，我作为尚书省的子代理，没有sessions_spawn工具。这是一个矛盾的情况：\n- 配置文件显示有权限\n- 但工具不可用\n\n现在我需要检查是否有其他方式来spawn，或者说明这是工具限制问题。\n\n让我尝试使用exec来检查是否有命令行工具可以spawn。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a7810f7895ad43dcafdc5c4d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which openclaw 2>/dev/null && openclaw --help 2>&1 | grep -i spawn || echo \"openclaw命令不支持spawn\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":3042,"output":365,"cacheRead":18240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21647,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774393159482}}
